data.eml:eml: A new species of Bathylepeta Moskalev, 1977 (Mollusca: Gastropoda) from the Weddell Sea, Antarctica

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Schwabe, Enrico (2006): A new species of Bathylepeta Moskalev, 1977 (Mollusca: Gastropoda) from the Weddell Sea, Antarctica. Zootaxa 1297: 37-45, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.173563
